        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;TUE MAY 13 | 7:30pm | Vancouver-based Raven Spirit Dance presents \\'Braiding the Land,\\' a trio of performances that follows three powerful female narratives to explore the physical, the spiritual, [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
