        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Don’t miss this stunningly beautiful film about the centrality of buffalo to Indigenous peoples, from award-winning Cree filmmaker Tasha Hubbard, director of NÎPAWISTAMÂSOWIN: WE WILL STAND UP, which screened at [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
