        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;Sat Nov 23 | Inspired by Christopher Dewdney’s award-winning book Acquainted with the Night, contemporary dancer and choreographer Shannon Litzenberger leads her multi-disciplinary creative team and ensemble of performers through [&hellip;]&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
